**Summary:**
This Japanese documentation explains how to use the Events Module in Amplitude charts, covering event addition (up to 10 events), default Amplitude events (Top Global Event, Segment Top Event, Any Active Event, Any Event, New Users), wildcard search functionality with asterisk/question mark/brackets operators, and event filtering using Filter by and Group by conditions with event properties and user properties.

